Subject: Need Assistance in File System Stale data review.
Description: Need to check FSAA / FSAC collected details.
What_We_Know__c: Initially the contact wast referring to the Higher level report.
Solution_Comment__c:
Symptom:
Need Assistance in File System Stale data review.
Cause:
Utilizing the wrong set of reports. 
Resolution:
Confirmed that the current version of Stealth application(s) running in the Environment:

Netwrix Enterprise Auditor (NEA)                11.6.0.89
Netwrix Access Information Center (AIC)    11.6.0.21
Netwrix Activity Monitor (NAM)                 7.1.151

Looked at the Netwrix Enterprise Auditor vl1.6 > Solutions > File System Solution > Cleanup Job Group > 1. Cleanup Assessment > FS_CleanupAssessmentJob(s)
https://helpcenter.netwrix.com/bundle/EnterpriseAuditor_11.6/page/Content/EnterpriseAuditor/Solutions/FileSystem/Cleanup/FS_CleanupAssessment.htm

Netwrix Enterprise Auditor vl1.6 > Administration > Application Maintenance and Best Practices > Updating Passwords
https://helpcenter.netwrix.com/bundle/EnterpriseAuditor_11.6/page/Content/EnterpriseAuditor/Admin/Maintenance/UpdatePasswords.htm

As well as pointed out an issue with access to the AIC. Noted o correct the access in the AIC for your account the other admin will need to update access via the Netwrix Access Information Center 11.6 > Administrator Overview > Configuration Interface Overview > Console Access Page
https://helpcenter.netwrix.com/bundle/AIC_11.6/page/Content/Access/InformationCenter/Admin/Configuration/ConsoleAccess.htm
